put.description:
RoleBinding defines the roles and actions a user can perform.
There are currently three roles (ADMIN, EDITOR, VIEWER).
User must exist before you can update its RoleBinding.
If you want to add a role binding for a user given the email address, call invite first to get a user id. Then call this endpoint.
